alists, the english are often made to feel unwelcome even treated as ousiders - invaders, (I am generalisng here) I think that is wrong. why can't people just exist side by side and get on with it?  The troubles in Ireland have been long and drawn out, it is about the english left them alone, I mean it is not as if england have an empire to keep anymore, what are they doing?<br>
